{"tid":1168193,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"倚天屠龍記女演員拒受婚姻束縛！","createTime":"2019-05-23T13:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T16:46:59.000Z","uid":74065,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f9a0c57dcf89e0d76624a254e82157d22b2155f5","tid":1168193,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190523/photo/bkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190523203355\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190523203355&h=982ce36b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由「周芷若」到「滅絕師太」，周海媚各方面都成熟不少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190523/photo/bkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190523203355\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190523203355&h=c0324a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周海媚直言唔鍾意受到婚姻束縛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190523/photo/bkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190523203355\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190523203355&h=41172f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話唔可以連出街都要畀人管住着乜嘢衫。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190523/photo/bkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190523203355\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190523%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190523203239805-0523_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190523203355&h=700f1813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高呼喜歡自由！<br />\n<br />\n藝人周海媚早前接受媒體訪問，笑談拍攝劇集《倚天屠龍記》由廿年前飾演周芷若，到現在飾演「滅絕師太」，當然各方面都成熟不少，亦覺得時間過得很快。談到婚姻話題，她耍手擰頭指自己不喜歡受到婚姻束縛：「如果連出街都要畀人管住着乜嘢衫，我唔可以，我喜歡自由。」<br />\n<br />\n至於曾有指她因血小板過低以致「不育」，她承認自己血小板低，生育確有大量出血的危險，而她每次拍拖都會同男友說清楚：「我會同對方講，我生育會有生命危險或者唔能夠生（BB），若果接受唔到就只好分開。」"},{"pid":"8246ef96b9803cbc742e2ce7c0d4c5abab0d8508","tid":1168193,"uid":254259,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:41:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4eb53c704df9ea0d1a01203f96b9cad912867c42","tid":1168193,"uid":46435,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"海味正能到撲街 勁想和她炒飯.."},{"pid":"53221fca0720415556cad614c6519810dd2e0b8f","tid":1168193,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:44:06.000Z","msg":"滿洲鑲白旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b5db4c7c23bf2fc83258e905b0cb20771fe9eb","tid":1168193,"uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eb53c704df9ea0d1a01203f96b9cad912867c42","tid":1168193,"uid":46435,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"海味正能到撲街 勁想和她炒飯.."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"52碎黎講都幾正🤔"},{"pid":"69d4d2b86f9327ec700b3836ac692d6c722586ff","tid":1168193,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"第一張圖唔講都真係唔知同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"758cea28eab9d344afe5ea2e9e32210ca949ccf1","tid":1168193,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69d4d2b86f9327ec700b3836ac692d6c722586ff","tid":1168193,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"第一張圖唔講都真係唔知同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T13:49:54.000Z","msg":"把閪口認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dddf60dc13a6e3fbcd61c1a8067246e8b426294b","tid":1168193,"uid":192307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quo